Package arcade

Class Main.Handler

java.lang.Object
arcade.Main.Handler
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.xml.sax.ContentHandler
Enclosing class:
Main
private static class Main.Handler
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.xml.sax.ContentHandler
Custom handler for parsing simulation setup XML.

The class checks for specific tags, which determine where the parsed data is placed for further processing by the Series class. Once the end tag for a given <series> is reached, a new Series object is instantiated. All content in the setup XML is stored as attribute-value pairs; there is no content between tags (the characters method is not used).

General structure of the XML file (attributes not listed): 

     <set>
         <series>
             <simulation>
                 <profilers>
                     <profiler />
                 </profilers>
                 <checkpoints>
                     <checkpoint />
                 </checkpoints>
             </simulation>
             <agents>
                 <populations>
                     <population>
                         <modules>
                             <module />
                         <modules>
                         <variables>
                             <variable />
                         <variables>
                     </population>
                     ...
                 </populations>
                 <helpers>
                     <helper />
                 </helpers>
             </agents>
             <environment>
                 <globals>
                     <global />
                 </globals>
                 <components>
                     <component />
                 </components>
             </environment>
         </series>
         ...
     </set>
